      <title>人民币防御压力加大 中国银行面临现金紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/chinese-banks-face-cash-squeeze-as-yuan-defence-adds-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在美元走强的情况下捍卫人民币汇率的决心日益增强，这加剧了该国的流动性紧缩状况，将关键的短期融资利率推至一年多以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/chinese-banks-face-cash-squeeze-as-yuan-defence-adds-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:57:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
